{"tid":914950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問：其實如果食到咁既賠率係咪可以必勝？","createTime":"2018-11-24T16:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T01:20:26.000Z","uid":153010,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7778691d360d6a12ff4de01023dd997209800134","tid":914950,"uid":153010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/235105_e6838d2123fb67f2873910d1a2af8f23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F235105_e6838d2123fb67f2873910d1a2af8f23.png&h=2eac0481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下半場大約60分鐘拜仁12.5角細馬會賣緊@1.97<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/235215_5b5e343c34c749bf2d74f331c7c62ac9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F235215_5b5e343c34c749bf2d74f331c7c62ac9.png&h=d2a38a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一邊廂Bet365同場12.5角大賣緊@2.1<br />\n如果真係捉到呢個時機<br />\n假設係馬會買1000蚊角細<br />\n再係Bet365買番950蚊角大<br />\n成本係$1950<br />\n開角細收$1970贏$20<br />\n開角大收$1995贏$45<br />\n開兩邊都有得贏？<br />\n可能呢場只係極端例子同埋買走地盤會有delay所以呢個諗法唔成立但我今朝發現澳職鳳凰果場事前飛都有同樣情況 <br />\n馬會賣11.5細@1.95<br />\nBet36511.5大賣2.1<br />\n其實周不時都會發現澳職俄超呢D聯賽既角球盤都有同出面莊家失衡既情況而且通常角細係會嚴重偏冷<br />\n如果真係咁買法係咪可以達致必勝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹新手一問求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd523fcd33e1dc67dec65e8c6d751ef27a48645","tid":914950,"uid":42396,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"啲飛射黎射去既姐<br />\n啲公司係玩食水位"},{"pid":"feb575380b1957aee2b9996009b095aa8094f269","tid":914950,"uid":153010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ded64684bf0da80b060f6577dc9dcf89f2b9508","tid":914950,"uid":153010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07af248b39fdc45729022de06cc